seo: Discuz,SQL注入,漏洞检测,faq.php,高危漏洞
summary: 该插件用于检测Discuz系统中是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定构造的HTTP请求并分析响应内容来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the Discuz system by sending specially crafted HTTP requests and analyzing the response content to confirm whether the vulnerability exists.
